scene.message:
Elly: We need to get{nl}
Maki's mom...{nl}
She should still be{nl}
at the shrine.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I'm Eri Kirishima.{nl}
I have someone injured.{nl}
Please open the gate.{waitkey}{ret}

Guard: No way! You can't{nl}
get in without{nl}
the password!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{wait_fr:16}I know.{nl}
"Walls have ears —{nl}
I am Mary."...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Will that do?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you're going to leave{nl}
Sonoda's mom alone?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Doesn't look like{nl}
they're letting{nl}
anyone through.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
Sonoda's mother worked{nl}
at SEBEC, right?{waitkey}Something smells off.{waitkey}{ret}
